org.pircbotx

Class ServerInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pircbotx.ServerInfo

  • public class ServerInfo
extends Object
    This is a giant info bean of various things about the server. This is separate from the PircBotX class due to its length

    Most info thanks to this great website on what each one does

    Note: On get methods that return int, -1 means the value exists but is unparsable natively

    Author:
    Leon Blakey
